- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the efficiency of existing methods and proposes a new interface to improve speed. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possibility as the paper focuses on designing a new interface for annotators. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possibility as the paper deals with annotating images with object labels.
